author: JerryRigEverything
description:
If the phrase "A man is only as good as his tools" is true... you're about to become invincible: https://www.iFixit.com/JerryRig

If you've ever wondered where JerryRigEverything gets his tool kits, wonder no more! My portable JerryRigEverything repair tool kit is here. Weather you want to repair grandmas glasses, your wristwatch, or the tiny screws inside your smartphone - this every day carry tool kit has the tools you need to get the job done!
title: The Greatest Collaboration in History is finally here
